Articles.Content:
Hi guys, this is JebKeb, the developer of the Proksolar mod. I've been away for a while because of email and password issues after the forum revamp.

I'm not a very new player - I bought the game in .18.2. I'm presently playing career with a space station being prepared to support a Duna transfer monster.

I'm going to continue on with Proksolar, and I am planning MORE!

  • Kopernicus real solar system (RSS doesn't work for me)
  • Valentina Kerman's Atomic Warheads and Nuclear Spacecraft Propulsors Co
  • Kerbwings Aerospace - bringing you avgas explosions since 1.0.4!
  • Jeb's Death Prevention
  • Kolonisation Komponents (self sustaining bases)
  • Interkellar (kopernicus other solar systems - like kerbalised rigel centaurus
  • RealAsteroids (explosion crater, bigger classes, gravity, better building destruction)
  • RealWeather (when quantum computers come out)

And probably more.

Anyway, thanks for reading, happy dockings!

 

Edited February 27, 2016 by JebKeb
